# =============================================================================
# SECTION 2: EF CORE / DATABASE
# Never commit migrations that haven't been reviewed, or any local DB files.
# Connection strings and secrets are handled in SECTION 5.
# =============================================================================

## SQLite local databases (if used in dev/testing)
*.db
*.db-shm
*.db-wal
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3

## EF Core snapshot backups (auto-generated, keep the main one)
## NOTE: Keep Migrations/ folder and ModelSnapshot.cs — they SHOULD be committed.
## Only ignore the backups and designer files.
**/Migrations/*Designer.cs

## Database seed data exports (local only)
**/SeedData/*.json
!**/SeedData/README.md


